# Test Bill Management Endpoints

## 1. Create Bill (Admin/Reception)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/bills
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "PATIENT_ID_HERE",
  "appointmentId": "APPOINTMENT_ID_HERE",
  "services": [
    {
      "name": "Consultation Fee",
      "cost": 500
    },
    {
      "name": "Blood Pressure Test",
      "cost": 200
    },
    {
      "name": "Medicines",
      "cost": 800
    }
  ],
  "totalAmount": 1500,
  "paymentMethod": "cash"
}

###

## 2. Get All Bills (with pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/bills?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

## 3. Get All Bills (filter by payment status)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/bills?paymentStatus=pending
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

## 4. Get Single Bill
GET http://localhost:5000/api/bills/BILL_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

## 5. Update Bill (Admin/Reception)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/bills/BILL_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentStatus": "paid",
  "paymentMethod": "upi",
  "paymentId": "pay_ABC123XYZ"
}

###

## 6. Download Bill PDF
GET http://localhost:5000/api/bills/pdf/BILL_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###
